mitmproxy
Interactive HTTPS proxy for traffic inspection

Sniffing & Spoofing
Description
mitmproxy is an interactive TLS-capable intercepting HTTP proxy. It can intercept, inspect, modify and replay web traffic for security testing.

Installation / Check
Check if installed:

which mitmproxy
Install command:

sudo apt install mitmproxy
Basic Syntax
mitmproxy
Common Commands
Command	What it does	When to use	Risk
mitmproxy

Launch interactive proxy	Intercept HTTP/S traffic	
mitmproxy -p 8080

Custom port	Different port	
mitmdump -w traffic.flow

Dump to file	Record traffic	
mitmweb

Web interface	Browser-based UI	
mitmdump -s script.py

With script	Automated modification	
